description: Enforce consistent data pipeline for life stats
globs:
  - "life_dashboard/lifestats/**/*.py"
  - "life_dashboard/services/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---

- All data updates must go through a single service layer (e.g., `update_stat`, `log_event`, `record_quest_progress`).
- Never manipulate stats directly in views or templates.
- Use the `StatValue`, `EventLog`, or `HabitLog` model for time-series tracking.
- Avoid circular dependencies between models (especially stats <-> skills <-> quests).


